---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
import ParallaxSection from '../components/ParallaxSection.astro';
import ScrollReveal from '../components/ScrollReveal.astro';
---

<Base title="历史">
  <ParallaxSection
    bgImage="/images/history-1.jpg"
    headingZh="海上丝绸之路"
    headingEn="The Maritime Silk Road"
    dark={true}
  >
    <ScrollReveal>
      <p style="color:rgba(255,255,255,0.85);">温州地处浙江东南沿海，自古就是海上丝绸之路的重要节点。宋代时期，温州港已是全国四大港口之一，商船远航至日本、东南亚和印度洋沿岸。</p>
      <p class="en-sub" style="color:rgba(255,255,255,0.6);text-transform:none;letter-spacing:0;">Wenzhou was one of China's four great ports during the Song Dynasty, with merchant ships reaching Japan, Southeast Asia, and the Indian Ocean.</p>
    </ScrollReveal>
  </ParallaxSection>

  <ParallaxSection
    bgImage="/images/history-2.jpg"
    headingZh="近代移民潮"
    headingEn="Modern Migration Waves"
  >
    <ScrollReveal>
      <p>19世纪末至20世纪初，第一批温州人远赴欧洲谋生。他们从街头小贩起步，逐渐建立起横跨法国、意大利、荷兰的商业网络。二战后的移民潮进一步扩大了温州的全球版图。</p>
      <p class="en-sub" style="text-transform:none;letter-spacing:0;">From the late 19th century, Wenzhou migrants built business networks across France, Italy, and the Netherlands, starting as street vendors.</p>
    </ScrollReveal>
  </ParallaxSection>

  <ParallaxSection
    bgImage="/images/history-3.jpg"
    headingZh="改革开放后的腾飞"
    headingEn="Rise After Reform and Opening"
    dark={true}
  >
    <ScrollReveal>
      <p style="color:rgba(255,255,255,0.85);">1978年后，温州成为中国民营经济的发源地之一。"温州模式"闻名全国，无数温州人走向世界，在全球130多个国家和地区建立了自己的事业。</p>
      <p class="en-sub" style="color:rgba(255,255,255,0.6);text-transform:none;letter-spacing:0;">After 1978, Wenzhou became the cradle of China's private economy. The "Wenzhou Model" spread globally across 130+ countries.</p>
    </ScrollReveal>
  </ParallaxSection>

  <ParallaxSection
    bgImage="/images/history-4.jpg"
    headingZh="新生代温州人"
    headingEn="The New Generation"
  >
    <ScrollReveal>
      <p>今天的年轻温州人活跃在科技、金融、艺术等各个领域。他们既传承着父辈的商业精神，又以全球化的视野开创新的可能。</p>
      <p class="en-sub" style="text-transform:none;letter-spacing:0;">Today's generation thrives in tech, finance, and the arts — carrying forward entrepreneurial traditions with a global perspective.</p>
    </ScrollReveal>
  </ParallaxSection>
</Base>

<script src="../scripts/parallax.js"></script>
<script src="../scripts/scroll-reveal.js"></script>
